        <title>[LO 5.3, 2.2]</title>
        <para id="id6221463">Let’s now <emphasis effect="bold">research </emphasis>some of nature’s <emphasis effect="italics">hidden treasures. </emphasis>Classify the following resources in the table below. This will give you a good idea of what a natural resource is and where it can be found.</para>
